title: [Icemule Trace, Exterior]
description: Winding around and between the giant conifers, the path is almost buried due to the snow that sloughs off the branches from time to time.  The darkness makes it difficult to navigate between the haunting silhouettes.

Winding around and between the giant conifers, the path is almost buried due to the snow that sloughs off the branches from time to time.  Dried pinecones, opened like blossoms, skitter across the glistening surface with each windy gust.
